{
  "texts": [
    "Further studies indicate that, despite the model is not capable to retrieve the exact sentence of the annotator (KGD Sentence), the retriever selects a sentence belonging to the same paragraph more than 69% of the time (KGD Paragraph).",
    "I, in different dialogue types: Open-Domain Dialogues (ODDs), Knowledge Grounded Dialogues (KGDs), Task-Oriented Dialogues (TODs), and Question Answering (QA).",
    "Results for fine-tuned models report mean and standard deviation over three runs.",
    "The code is available at https://github.com/ sislab-unitn/Fine-Tune-or-Rag",
    "The extended protocol is available at https://github."
  ]
}